    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《困住：家庭假期》是一款结合生存元素的找茬类恐怖游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >平均游戏时间：120-240分钟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在一家酒店里。回顾旧的摄像头录像，探索房间，找出不同。但要小心——每个房间都有住客，并且都有自己的规则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个房间的摄像头录像中找出五处不同以完成任务。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/050cdb68d1eb0f572667dce15591e651.poster.avif?t=1754601320\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/050cdb68d1eb0f572667dce15591e651.webm?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/050cdb68d1eb0f572667dce15591e651.mp4?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过找出继家族成员和玩具的行为模式和规则来生存下去。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/90eed2e7036affdf92f06c0642daea6f.poster.avif?t=1754601320\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/90eed2e7036affdf92f06c0642daea6f.webm?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/90eed2e7036affdf92f06c0642daea6f.mp4?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
